name: The Processed measurement contains all the requested data
description:
A default measurement should include:

- `attempts`
- `skippedPulseDetection`
- `skippedFingerDetection`
- `skippedMovementDetection`
- `technical_details`
- `heartrate`
- `quadrants`
- `time_vector`

All extra enabled data (like motion data) is also be added
